law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 4, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1986. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 145, sec. 21, effective June 16, 1972.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Preliminary expenses of turnpike projects - Leases between authority and bureau authorized - Hazards caused by weather - Bureau to alleviate.
